## ğŸ“¦ How to Use This Package

### Step 1: Read Documentation (Pick One Path)

**Path A: Fast Integration** (~5 min)
```
QUICK_START.md â†’ Copy files â†’ Run â†’ Done
```

**Path B: Full Understanding** (~1 hour)
```
