## ğŸ¤” FAQ

**Q: Do I need to use all features?**
A: No! Each is independent. Use what you need.

**Q: Will this work with my existing code?**
A: Yes! The design is modular and non-intrusive.

**Q: How long to implement?**
A: 10-15 minutes for basic integration, 1-2 hours for full customization.

**Q: Can I use with real SCADA?**
A: Yes! The simulator tests strategies. Deploy executor to real systems.

**Q: How much training data needed?**
A: Works with zero data initially. Improves with each cycle.

**Q: Is the code production-ready?**
A: Yes! Error handling, logging, and validation included.

